=聖朝佐闢=
written by [[許大受]], probably composed in 1623 (Dudnik, 110)

* Many passages translated by Gernet in //Chine et Christianisme, action et réaction// (Paris: Gallimard, 1982)

* Adrian Dudink: The Sheng-ch'ao tso-p'i (1623) of Hsü Ta-shou. In: Conflict and accomodation in early modern East Asia: Essays in Honour of Erik Zürcher. Leiden: Brill, 2003.